g.text: usage: fu-split [-h] -i INPUT [-I INPUT_REV] -o OUTPUT [--for-tag FOR_TAG]
Split FASTA/FASTQ files into multiple files
-h, --help show this help message and exit
Output file (add a stretch of 3+ zeroes to specify the
progressive number), compression will be detected.
--for-tag FOR_TAG Tag to use for the forward reads output (default: _R1
--rev-tag REV_TAG Tag to use for the forward reads output (default: _R2
--version show program's version number and exit
Character used to represent the progressive number in
--compress Force compression of the output files
--bin BIN Seqfu binary, can be $SEQFU_BIN [deafault: seqfu]
